feed.title: Fisk Lab at URI
feed.subtitle: The Fisk Lab is a dry-lab at URI focused on using "basic science" methods from evolution, population genetics, genomics, and bioinformatics as tools for translational research. We also pusure Discipline-Based Education Research (DBER) for Computational Biology

entry.title: Fisk Lab Happenings Fall 2024
entry.content:
Post In Progress

This fall the Fisk Lab has been busy! Welcome Amanda to the lab!
